case_data.summary:
[This summary is temporary while we research this case.]

On September 30, 2025, plaintiff filed suit in U.S. District Court for the District of Massachusetts. Plaintiff claims the SSA is working with ICE to facilitate the SSA's own sharing of immigrants' taxpayer information in contravention of the confidentiality protections of the Tax Reform Act of 1976.

This case is ongoing.
